OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FRed weather warnings are continuing
OL,7,Finto Friday following several days of
OL,8,Frecord-breaking temperatures for June.
OL,10,FSeveral hospitals have declared
OL,11,Fcritical incidents amid the heatwave,
OL,12,Fwith University Hospital Southampton
OL,13,Fbeing forced to cancel a number of
OL,14,Fplanned operations and some outpatient
OL,15,Fappointments.
OL,17,FQueen Alexandra Hospital in Portsmouth
OL,18,Fand Norfolk and Norwich University
OL,19,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust both
OL,20,Fdeclared critical incidents on
OL,21,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
