OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FAs football fans prepare to cheer for
OL,7,FEngland during Saturday's Fifa World
OL,8,FCup game, chief operating officer
OL,9,FCraig Harman has told people to drink
OL,10,Fresponsibly.
OL,12,FHe advised people to drink "plenty of
OL,13,Fwater" in between alcoholic beverages.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
