PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782487105
OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FThe chief said that it is not just the
OL,7,Felderly and people with underlying
OL,8,Fhealth conditions affected by the
OL,9,Fheat, adding: "I'm saying to people I
OL,10,Fneed you to drink water even when
OL,11,Fyou're not thirsty, staying out of the
OL,12,Fsun during the hottest parts of the
OL,13,Fday, and particularly not exercising
OL,14,Foutside and putting your body under
OL,15,Fadditional heat and strain."
OL,17,FEmergency services
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@\O]
