OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FOn Thursday evening, firefighters in
OL,7,FDerbyshire continued battling a 500-
OL,8,Fsquare-metre wildfire on Tintwistle
OL,9,FMoor, with video showing billowing
OL,10,Fsmoke and flames consuming trees.
OL,12,FThe London Ambulance Service (LAS)
OL,13,Fresponded to its highest number of
OL,14,Flife-threatening emergencies ever on
OL,15,FWednesday, and Mr Harman said they
OL,16,Fexpect "demand to grow day on day over
OL,17,Fthe next couple of days".
OL,26,@xD@HOUyD@XO]
