OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FLAS saw a 50% increase in life-
OL,7,Fthreatening emergency calls compared
OL,8,Fwith a typical Wednesday in June, with
OL,9,Fthe number of cardiac arrests up 30%.
OL,11,F'Heat-dome' conditions
OL,13,FThe current heatwave is driven by a
OL,14,F"heat-dome" ` an area of high pressure
OL,15,Fthat stalls over a region and traps
OL,16,Fheat ` settling over western Europe
OL,17,Fand bringing extreme conditions across
OL,18,Fthe continent.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
