OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FHuman-driven climate change, mostly
OL,7,Fcaused by burning fossil fuels, is
OL,8,Fmaking such extreme heatwaves more
OL,9,Ffrequent and intense.
OL,11,FITV News explains the 'heat-dome' that
OL,12,Fhas descended on Europe
OL,14,FWarnings continue into weekend
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
