OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FEarlier, the Met Office extended its
OL,7,Fred warning until 9pm on Friday for
OL,8,FLondon and parts of east and South
OL,9,FEast England, stretching across
OL,10,FOxfordshire and Bedfordshire,
OL,11,FHampshire and Kent ` the first time it
OL,12,Fhas issued red heat warnings over
OL,13,Fthree consecutive days.
OL,15,FAmber heat warnings are in place for a
OL,16,Fwider area on Friday, and are running
OL,17,Finto Saturday for parts of east and
OL,18,Fsouth-east England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
