OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FA yellow warning is in place for
OL,7,Fthunderstorms for south-west England
OL,8,Fon Thursday night, while swathes of
OL,9,FScotland, England, Wales and Northern
OL,10,FIreland face yellow warnings for
OL,11,Fthunderstorms on Friday.
OL,13,FEastern England is expected to see the
OL,14,Fhighest temperatures on Friday, she
OL,15,Fadded, but things will "finally cool
OL,16,Fdown this weekend", according to Annie
OL,17,FShuttleworth, a Met Office
OL,18,Fmeteorologist.
OL,26,@wD@XOUxD@RO]
