OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FWales has seen its hottest June day on
OL,7,Frecord on Thursday, with 35.9C
OL,8,Frecorded in Cardiff, meanwhile,
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland has seen the previous
OL,10,Frecord high for June matched after a
OL,11,Ftemperature of 30.8C was reached in
OL,12,FCastlederg.
OL,14,FThe National Energy System Operator
OL,15,F(NESO) issued an electricity margin
OL,16,Fnotice ` which calls on companies to
OL,17,Fmake additional capacity available `
OL,18,Ffor Friday evening due to the
OL,19,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
