OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782487105
OL,3,CRed weather warnings remain in place
OL,4,Cas hospitals declare critical incidents
OL,6,FA NESO spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,Fforecasts are showing tight margins on
OL,8,Fthe electricity system for tomorrow
OL,9,Fevening (Friday).
OL,11,F"An Electricity Margin Notice (EMN)
OL,12,Fhas been issued to the market. This is
OL,13,Fa routine tool, and means we are
OL,14,Fasking market participants to make any
OL,15,Fadditional generation capacity they
OL,16,Fmay have available.
OL,18,F"The EMN does not mean electricity
OL,19,Fsupply is at risk."
OL,21,FMosquito warnings
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@AOUzD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
